---
title: Hoisin Veggie Mince Udon Noodles with Tenderstem® Broccoli and Carrot
description: This delicious Hoisin Veggie Mince Udon Noodles has been expertly designed by our chefs as a lighter option to help with a balanced lifestyle.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R25_W34_UK_QR18418-9_Main_edit_high-2e94b4ae.jpg
